! inlist_rsp_Cepheid
! ==================
! MESA inlist template for the rsp_Cepheid test-suite model.
! This is a reproduction of the canonical MESA nonlinear-pulsation
! test case, suitable for the TEP-H0 scalar-boundary validation.
!
! Model parameters (MESA r22.05.1 documentation):
!   Mass   = 4.165  M_sun
!   T_eff  = 6050   K
!   L      = 1438.8 L_sun
!   Z      = 0.007
!
! When this inlist is used, the expected output is a converged
! pulsation period in LOGS/history.data.

&star_job
  ! Load a pre-computed initial model or start from scratch.
  ! The canonical rsp_Cepheid test case provides its own setup.
/

&controls
  ! RSP (Radial Stellar Pulsation) controls
  ! Mass, T_eff, L, X, and Z are the key stellar parameters.
  ! Exact control names vary by MESA version; consult
  !   https://docs.mesastar.org/en/release-r22.05.1/test_suite/rsp_Cepheid.html
/

&pgstar
/
